
Just run the following command:

   packs formamide.gro spce_oplsaa.wtr -nm 2500 -cc 1.0 -it -bk

This will create:

   formamide+spce_mol2500.gro
   formamide+spce_mol2500.top
   formamide+spce_mol2500.zip

To visualize the simulation box, try:

   sview formamide+spce_mol2500.gro
   jmol formamide+spce_mol2500.gro
   vmd formamide+spce_mol2500.gro

To test the simulation box, try:

   mdrun formamide+spce_mol2500.gro -chk

